      <div class="t8-photo-ph-text">WORKHORSE T8 PRODUCT PHOTOGRAPHY<br><span style="opacity:0.5;">— ROOSTER CREATIVE DELIVERABLE —</span><br><br><span style="opacity:0.5;">DIP-SWITCH DETAIL · LAMP BODY · 4FT</span></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="t8-eyebrow t8-eyebrow-rule" style="opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;"><span class="t8-accent-text">TUBUL<span class="aa">Ⓐ</span>RCH ·</span> LINEAR LED RETROFIT · T8 · 4FT G13 BIPIN</p>
      <h1 id="t8-hero-h1" class="t8-h1" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,3.75rem);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">The Workhorse T8</h1>
