        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.7;">G13 bipin · F32T8 / F28T8</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1.5px solid rgba(17,17,17,0.15);background:white;text-align:left;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--t8-mono);font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">HIGH OUTPUT</p>
        <p style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">T8 HO (4ft)</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.7;">G13 bipin · F32T8/HO</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1.5px solid rgba(17,17,17,0.15);background:white;text-align:left;">
