        <p style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">T12 Fluorescent (4ft)</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.7;">G13 bipin · F40T12</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border:1.5px solid rgba(17,17,17,0.15);background:white;text-align:left;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--t8-mono);font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;opacity:0.6;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">DIRECT WIRE</p>
        <p style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Ballast Bypass (Type B)</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.7;">Line voltage · no ballast</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <style>
      @media (max-width: 768px) { .t8-wizard-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important; } }
      @media (max-width: 480px) { .t8-wizard-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; } }
    </style>
    <p style="font-family:var(--t8-mono);font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;opacity:0.5;">ALL FOUR TYPES SUPPORTED · SAME SKU · TYPE A (BALLAST-COMPATIBLE) + TYPE B (BYPASS) IN ONE LAMP</p>
