          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>L70 life</dt><dd>&gt;50,000 hours (TM-21, 35°C ambient)</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p class="t8-spec-block-num" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">03</p>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Electrical</h3>
        <dl>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Input voltage</dt><dd>120–277V AC · 50/60 Hz</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Wattage (dip-switch)</dt><dd>10.5W · 12W · 14W · 15W · 18W</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Power factor</dt><dd>&gt;0.90</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>THD</dt><dd>&lt;20%</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Inrush current</dt><dd>≤30A peak (see Engineering Candor note)</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Start time</dt><dd>&lt;0.5 s to full output</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p class="t8-spec-block-num" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">04</p>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Retrofit Type</h3>
        <dl>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Type A (ballast-compatible)</dt><dd>Works with electronic T8 ballasts · no rewiring</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Type B (bypass)</dt><dd>Direct line-voltage wiring · ballast removed</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Hybrid</dt><dd>Same SKU supports both Type A and Type B</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Ballast compatibility</dt><dd>200+ models tested · see Ballast Compatibility List</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p class="t8-spec-block-num" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">05</p>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Controls &amp; Dimming</h3>
        <dl>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Default driver</dt><dd>0-10V dimmable · 10–100% smooth · no flicker at 1 kHz</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Compatible controls</dt><dd>Lutron EcoSystem · nLight · Wattstopper DLM · Acuity nLight Air</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Sensor-ready /SR variant</dt><dd>Plug-N-Play motion-sensor receptacle · NLC stand<span class="aa">Ⓐ</span>RCH protocol</dd></div>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Dim-to-off behavior</dt><dd>Cleanly off at 0V · no end-of-life flicker</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p class="t8-spec-block-num" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">06</p>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;">Compliance &amp; Listings</h3>
        <dl>
          <div class="t8-spec-row"><dt>Safety</dt><dd>UL 1598C · CSA · cULus Listed</dd></div>
